    why1: 'In recent years, the number of women requesting information about intimate area conditions has increased. We have incorporated the services of <strong class="font-bold underline text-zeniaRosaOscuro">Dr. Romaguera</strong>, specialist in <strong class="font-bold underline text-zeniaRosaOscuro">Gynaeco-aesthetics</strong>, to address functional problems, treat any related pathology and help with intimate feminine beauty.',
