    training1: '<strong class="font-bold underline text-zeniaRosaOscuro">Aesthetic and regenerative</strong> gynaecology is a new specialty where few professionals are sufficiently qualified. At our clinic we help you achieve the best results thanks to the advice of <strong class="font-bold underline text-zeniaRosaOscuro">Dr. Romaguera</strong>.',
